Package frc.alotobots

Class Constants.CanId

java.lang.Object
frc.alotobots.Constants.CanId
Enclosing class:
Constants
public static final class Constants.CanId extends Object
CAN bus device ID assignments. This class maps CAN IDs for all motors, sensors and other CAN-connected devices.
